This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for learning multilingual word embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses word2vec and deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which fall under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper uses a concept-based approach, which is related to deep learning and falls under the sub-category of cs.DL (Deep Learning).
